DNS record types: A, AAAA, CNAME, MX, MXE, TXT, URL, URL301, FRAME

Environment:
  NAMECHEAP_API_USER             API username
  NAMECHEAP_API_KEY              API key
  NAMECHEAP_USERNAME             Account username (default: same as API_USER)
  NAMECHEAP_CLIENT_IP            Whitelisted IP (auto-detected if not set)
  NAMECHEAP_API_URL              API URL (default: production)
  NAMECHEAP_SANDBOX              Set to 1 for sandbox mode

Examples:
  agent-namecheap domains
